{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"B\n    \n      Domain-Partitioned Sources + Delta Live Tables ⭐ Recommended\n      The generator writes to domain-specific staging Delta tables (order_events, inventory_events, etc.). A Spark Declarative Pipeline (DLT) defines each MVM table as a @dlt.table with readStream, expectations, and FK enrichment. Deployed via Databricks Asset Bundle.\n      \n        Pros\n          DLT handles checkpointing, retries, and lineage\n          Built-in data quality expectations per table\n          Scales per-domain independently\n          Full DAB deployment (bundle.yml declares pipeline + jobs)\n          Clean separation: generate → stage → transform → serve\n        \n        Cons\n          More moving parts (staging tables + DLT pipeline)\n          DLT adds pipeline compute cost\n        \n      \n      \n        Generator Job → Staging Tables (per domain) → DLT Pipeline (readStream per table) → MVM Silver Tables → Gold Metrics Views","choice":"b","id":null,"timestamp":1778858045935}
